---
// Hero section - central domain framing
---

<section class="mb-16 md:mb-20">
  <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:items-end">
    <div>
      <p class="font-mono text-sm text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-5">
        heybeaux.dev / root domain
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[0.98] max-w-4xl text-[var(--color-ink)]">
        Beaux builds the thing between the idea and the working system.
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6 md:p-7 bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.72)]">
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-5">
        This is the central index for my products, labs, agent infrastructure, and client work.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-6">
        Ginnung, Sonder, and AWM can keep their own universe. Wavelength, DripCtl, The Trash Panda, and whatever comes next get room to look and sound like themselves.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="#projects" class="btn inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white font-medium rounded">
          Explore projects
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@heybeaux.dev" class="btn inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 border border-[var(--color-border)] text-[var(--color-text)] font-medium rounded bg-white">
          Start a conversation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="border-l-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] pl-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-1">Now</p>
      <p class="font-medium">Agent systems, SaaS tools, Salesforce integrations</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-l-2 border-[#8B5CF6] pl-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-1">Base</p>
      <p class="font-medium">Powell River, BC · Pacific time</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-l-2 border-[#D97706] pl-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-1">Mode</p>
      <p class="font-medium">Build fast, keep it useful, make it legible</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
